div.div:
Lee Han, a Graduate student, was reborn as the youngest son in another world’s famous family of mages.
He swore he would never go to another place with the word “academy” in it. However, the magic academy known as Einrogard completely ignored what he had promised himself.
Being independent is a must; monsters may appear, and the professors are all nutjobs! The beginning of a pathetic academy life that you have never seen before.
Life as a magic academy mage, “Will I be able to… graduate safely?”

As a powerful 8th class mage, Ian Paige took countless innocent lives under the orders of Emperor Ragnar, a close friend and ruler of the Greenriver Empire. Yet despite their closeness, Ragnar views Ian as a threat and subsequently poisons him. Using time magic, Ian saves himself and returns 30 years to the past. Now a young boy, Ian joins an elite order of mages to hone his abilities once again. This time, he’ll get revenge on the emperor who betrayed him and reclaim glory as an 8th class mage!
(Source: Tapas)
